es.upm.gib.eutilsrdfwrapper.motor
Class Results

java.lang.Object
  es.upm.gib.eutilsrdfwrapper.motor.Results

public class Results
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents the dynamic retrieval of results from NCBI, related to a specific query. Objects of this class do not hold results, but rather allow us to retrieve the results of a query. Due to restrictions in the NCBI design, results are not given all at a time, but rather must be requested in small groups. This class adapts that functionality and offers a method for asking if there are more available results, and obtaining one more result.
